{"id": "art-1531", "label": "Art. 1531", "title": "Art. 1531", "slug": "art-1531", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2092449444\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1212\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2092449444\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_474283922\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1211\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_474283922\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Concediul paternal</i>\neste concediul acordat tat&#259;lui copilului nou-n&#259;scut în\ncondi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute de Legea concediului paternal nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>210/1999</span><span style='color:black'>, cu\nmodific&#259;rile &#351;i complet&#259;rile ulterioare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1836438427\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1210\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1836438427\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Concediul de\nîngrijitor</i> este concediul acordat salaria&#355;ilor în vederea oferirii de\nîngrijire sau sprijin personal unei rude sau unei persoane care locuie&#351;te\nîn aceea&#351;i gospod&#259;rie cu salariatul &#351;i care are nevoie de\nîngrijire sau sprijin ca urmare a unei probleme medicale grave.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1283533322\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1209\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1283533322\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Îngrijitor</i>\neste salariatul care ofer&#259; îngrijire sau sprijin personal unei rude sau\nunei persoane care locuie&#351;te în aceea&#351;i gospod&#259;rie cu salariatul\n&#351;i care are nevoie de îngrijire sau sprijin ca urmare a unei probleme\nmedicale grave.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1780240737\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1208\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1780240737\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)În sensul art. 152<sup>1</sup> alin. (1), precum &#351;i\nal alin. (3), prin rud&#259; se în&#355;elege fiul, fiica, mama, tat&#259;l sau\nso&#355;ul/so&#355;ia unui salariat.</span></p>"}